    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "bdd2329a-fe90-4191-8d5f-ed66f93a27d1",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "BCR VOL. 14 - JACKSONVILLE",
        "Location": "LOCATION_BANGKOK",
        "PublicId": "108308260089",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Bangkok/_scene_tiger.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository fd5e4b5f-ade1-4323-8622-823b48685b9f).Image",
        "Description": "Agent 47,\rWelcome to Bangkok, where luxury meets lunacy. Your mission?\rFive targets: Jackie, Jack, Jack, Jack, and—wait for it—Jackie. \rYes, it’s as confusing as it sounds, but who are we to judge their parents’ creativity?\r\rThese five have turned the hotel into their playground, strutting like royalty and arguing over who’s the “real Jack.” The staff’s patience is gone, and so is the minibar. Time to restore order, 47—quietly, cleanly, and without a trace.\r\rGood luck.\r\rCheers,\rBuuurgers",
